Specific installation instruction
=================================

  This project contains a Foswiki plugin (see http://foswiki.org for 
more information about it). To install it, you must first create the 
plugin archive :

    1. `./configure`

       Eventually you can set the metaserver WebName using the 
       --with-webname='AnotherWikiName'. Default for webname is
       'Meta'.

    2. `make plugin` to create the package

    3. mv the created archive to your foswiki root directory.

    4. `tar --strip-components=1 -xvzpf <plugin_archive_name>.

    5. Activate the plugin using fowiki's configure script.
